content.rendered:
Directed by Qasim Khallow.

Written by Sumit Gupt. Qasim Khallow. Qasim Khallow. Qasim Khallow.

Cast Alisha(Dancer). Deepika Amin(Deboshree). Malvika Bajaj(Judge). Ashish Bhatt(Bhavesh). Ashish Bhatt(Bhavesh). Riam Biswas(Dancer). Sandipa Das(Sanjana). Bharti Doshi(Massi). Sangeeta Duttaa(Dancer). Kumar Kanchan Ghosh(Acharya). Forum Gothecha(Judge). Gyaneshwar Gyani(Prasanjeet). Kalyani Jha(Sulagana). Brijendra Kala(Alok). Shashi Kiran(Pandit Ji). Chandan Kumar(Shopkeeper). Jitendra Kumar(Srijoy). Umesh Kumar(Rickshaw Driver). Shreya Lama(Kid On Cycle). Aniket More(Boy 1). Anil Mundhra(Host). Rajani Mundhra(Female Customer @ Mall). Mukesh Pandey(Authority). Sahil Patel(Dr. Bhisma Bhattacharya). Govind Pathak(Rambabu). Sarita Patil(Patient Mom). Laxmi Pillai(Teacher). Suhani Popli(Priyanka). Pawan Raj(Husband(Female Customer) (as Pawan Raj Nayan)). Trilok Sadhwani(Backstage Manager). Kalpana Sarkar(Recepetionist). Titly Sarkar(Dancer). Shikha Sarsar(Female Customer @ HR Msrket). Tikkum Sharma(Judge). Vipin Sharma(Anup). Priyamvada Singh(Alka). Kajal Thakur(E’s School Friend). Rajan Tiwari(Dr. Shashi Kundu) .

Language Hindi.

Producers Qasim Khallow. Rudraksh Pandya. Vijay Rozera.

Production DNG Films. Eros Worldwide.
